As a self-taught designer, I've dedicated myself to mastering User Experience and User Interface design out of sheer passion. With over 10,000 hours invested directly into crafting digital products, I firmly believe in the pivotal role of user-centric design. For me, it's not just about the intricacy, but the meticulousness and clarity of the user research that drives the design forward.

My approach revolves around not just acquiring design knowledge and user insights, but also synthesizing and interpreting them to uncover clear design drivers for concept development. Every decision I make is anchored in a deep understanding of both the business goals and the needs of the customer.

Steps for completing your project

After purchasing the project, send requirements so Muqarrab can start the project.

Delivery time starts when Muqarrab receives requirements from you.

Muqarrab works on your project following the steps below.

Requirement Finalization

The requirements will be finalized in a document detailing all the colors and fonts to be used in Shopify website.

Create wireframes

Review the work, release payment, and leave feedback to Muqarrab.
